<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #0056b3;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .benefits {
      background: #e9ecef;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Syrnyk, {{firstName}}!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Thank you for joining our community! We are happy to have you among our customers.</p>

      <div class="benefits">
        <h3>Your benefits as a registered customer:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Easily track your orders</li>
          <li>Save your delivery preferences</li>
          <li>Get access to exclusive offers</li>
          <li>Fast checkout process</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>You can now log in to your account to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>View your order history</li>
        <li>Update your profile information</li>
        <li>Manage your delivery addresses</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact us.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>Your Syrnyk Team</p>
      
      <!-- Logo section with fallback -->
      <div style="margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;">
        <img src="{{frontendUrl}}/assets/logo2.png" alt="SYRNYK"
          style="max-width: 150px; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto;"
          onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';" />
        <div style="display: none; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #0056b3; padding: 10px;">
          ðŸ§€ SYRNYK
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>